					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Failure to do so will cause the genitalia to be ripped out from the body <strong>of the nearest male and female human from SCP-4828</strong>.</p> </blockquote> <p>Edit made. (I'm not really sure with the grammar though.)<br /> Thank you for spotting that.</p> <blockquote> <p>I wish you would’ve included more in the Spells Addendum, but that’s just my thoughts.</p> </blockquote> <p>I <em>think</em> I can add some more.</p> <p>Thank you for your upvote!</p> 
				 	]]>
