					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Real weird, but I enjoyed it. I wish you would’ve included more in the Spells Addendum, but that’s just my thoughts.</p> <p>One part could use some clarification however,</p> <blockquote> <p>Failure to do so will cause the genitalia to be ripped out from the person’s body.</p> </blockquote> <p>One, <em>ouch</em>, but who’s genitalia? The nearest person, as with some of the other effects?</p> <p>Nevertheless, this gets my vote.</p> 
				 	]]>
