					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10358234#post-4160131</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10358234/scp-4828#post-4160131</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 21 Feb 2019 06:24:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Pelumo 64</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2818192</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>As a said in my critique I'm not only happy to see this on the main site but proud to know that my commentaries and remarks helped shape such a fine job.</p> <p>When it comes to the SCP all I can say is: A good concept done in a remarkable manner reminiscing of early works in terms of simplicity and effectiveness in a nice straightforward manner.</p> <p>When it comes to the author I can say: I really hope to see more of your works in the early future. Who knows, maybe The Multistore from Nowhere and Everywhere becomes the next big GOI and maybe you take off as a writer and become part of the wiki's history as one of the great ones. Whatever you do next is yours to decide and in the end, you will find that the only and final limit is yourself, but no matter what you do remember that sometimes you need to look back in order to move forward.</p> <p>Edit: Sorry, when I saw that this was published I had to rush to the discussion to make a comment and apparently forgot to upvote, something I didn't forget to do was archiving this one in my personal collection.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
